'''[[quaternary]] [[ammonium]] [[compound]]'''
#{{chemistry}} an amine [[derivative]], containing four [[radical]]s, of [[general formula]] R<sub>1</sub>R<sub>2</sub>R<sub>3</sub>R<sub>4</sub>-N<sup>+</sup>X<sup>-</sup>; the radicals may be the same, different, or part of a ring; X is any [[univalent]] [[cation]] such as OH<sup>-</sup>
